## **Document Metadata**

### Required Frontmatter

All documentation should include:
```yaml
---
type: [sop|requirement|feature|guide|architecture]
title: "Document Title"
created: YYYY-MM-DD
updated: YYYY-MM-DD
status: [draft|review|approved|deprecated]
---
```



