## **Validation**

### Commands
```bash
# Validate all documentation
sc validate --docs

# Validate cross-references
sc validate --docs --cross-refs

# Validate document placement
sc validate --docs --placement

# Validate indexes
sc validate --docs --indexes

# Fix broken references
sc validate --docs --fix-refs
```

### What Gets Validated
- ✅ Frontmatter present and valid
- ✅ Internal links resolve
- ✅ Cross-references exist
- ✅ Document in correct location
- ✅ INDEX.md complete (if 5+ files)
- ✅ Naming conventions followed

